Faustina Ampah nwere FIFA World Cup mbụ ya na 2012 FIFA U-20 Women's World Cup nke Japan kwadoro na 2012

Egwuregwu izizi ya bụ megide United States nke mechiri 4:0 na ihu ọma nke United States. Faustina Ampah sokwa na 2014 FIFA U-20 Women's World Cup na 2016 FIFA U-20 women's World cup na-eme ka ọ bụrụ naanị onye Ghana na-anọchite anya mba ahụ na FIFA U-20 World Cup atọ
Egwuregwu asọmpi mbụ Ampah maka otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Ghana bụ 2018 WAFU Women's Cup
Ọ gbara bọọlụ n'egwuregwu ise niile nke asọmpi ahụ nyere Black Queens aka inweta ọkwa mbụ
O meriri ndị otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Naịjirịa
Ọ meriri onye ọkpụkpọ nke egwuregwu ahụ n'egwuregwu ahụ.
